# Fixture 3D architecture

- GDTF is Z-up; presentation root applies `-90° X` for Three.js Y-up viewer
- `localTransform` stored in GDTF Z-up metres; UI uses `fixtureTransform.ts` for mm↔m
- Assembly rebuilds on `assemblyRevision` bump — not mid gizmo drag
- `fixtureAssembly.ts` tags groups with `userData.partId` for raycast selection
- Save: `PUT /api/fixtures/:id` with full `definition` JSON after transform edits
- Pan/tilt: Yoke on pan (GDTF Z), Head on tilt (GDTF X, tracks pan via hierarchy)
